<section class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 bg-carbon-black text-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
      No más café desperdiciado.
      <span class="text-white/60">Solo preparaciones excepcionales.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white/90 mb-16 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Únete a miles de amantes del café que ya dominan el arte de la preparación perfecta.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
      <button class="bg-white text-carbon-black px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-xl">
        Descargar en App Store
      </button>
      <button class="bg-transparent text-white border-2 border-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300">
        Descargar en Google Play
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
